{"tid":976313,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"「悲報」騰訊投資《戰鎚：Vermintide》系列研發商 Fatshark","createTime":"2019-01-10T10:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T12:00:44.000Z","uid":58120,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5d26d0a7b62eb1e9767627d678fde5de47d551","tid":976313,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"根據瑞典網路媒體 DI Digital 報導，中國廠商騰訊已經收購了《戰鎚：Vermintide》的瑞典研發商 Fatshark 大量股份。<br />\n <br />\nFatshark 曾經開發過《逃離死亡之島》、《玫瑰戰爭》等作品，最近研發的《戰鎚：Vermintide》系列受到不少玩家歡迎。<br />\n <br />\n根據報導指出，騰訊以約 5600 萬美元收購了 Fatshark 36% 的股份。Fatshark 表示，接受騰訊的投資將會強化其作為獨立開發商的地位，並有助於促進研發團隊未來的成長，而他們不變的使命是為了全球玩家帶來高品質的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母騰訊唔好再搞尻遊戲界啦</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3c457a0a672376a35637964d68e58235c5a98de5","tid":976313,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"而他們不變的使命是為了全球玩家帶來高品質的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不變的使命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1605e1c7280f822177d48452b018e738bd93ff","tid":976313,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"ok，番屋企delete game，反正好多Game都仲未有時間玩"},{"pid":"52c4428f1f1de19ae43b34e8dd9c20321146e8b4","tid":976313,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母騰訊唔好再搞尻遊戲界啦</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n有D野雙向，前幾日買隻電話game，見香港同美國app store唔同developer，以為有人偷野，點知睇番佢game development blog話呢D支那公司可以幫佢地係支那市場賣多D game，咁人地想賺多D錢都無錯嘅"},{"pid":"81c882a6b3359ecc225580629317dc96ca18dbc1","tid":976313,"uid":7524,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52c4428f1f1de